Text: To come all the way to New York|just to get hit with a bowel attack...
This one's worse than|that one up in Alaska...
that commander chick really|reminds me of someone...
Now that's a time I'd like to forget...
Ridiculous that I had to get jacked|for everything that was on me...
that's when everything|started to hit the skids...
...up to that point I was steady|cruising on the elite course...
Still, that Russian crew is|a pretty decent bunch...
The President's escort guys|get on my nerves though...
...for now, just gotta hang in there...
